data.description: Beautiful Farmhouse on a 10,000 SF corner lot with tons of charm! It offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, a huge kitchen with hardwood floors, and enough space for a big table or an island. New Smart-Refrigerator. Separate formal Dining Room and Living Room. Newer carpet, washer and dryer. Walking distance to Maple Park's downtown and schools. Close to Randall Road, shopping, and restaurants.
